{
  "title": "Colorful Festive Syrian Vegetable Pilaf",
  "description": "A floral and velvety Syrian dish featuring peanut oil and poached vegetables, perfect for a plant-based friendly meal. This recipe is a great way to experience the flavors of Syria in a festive and healthy way.",
  "cuisine": "Syrian",
  "diet": [
